commit.message: Move `VectorizerMixin` import to the top of file.
New default argumnets for `LogisticRegression`, `LogisticRegressionCV` and `RFECV`
Default value of `gamma` in `sklearn.svm.*` changed from `auto` to `scale`
`VectorizerMixin` is no longer base class for `CountVectorizer`
`random_state` is depracted in `OneClassSVM`
